    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and it is honestly such a gem! It's been super well-loved and is in really solid shape, ready to hit the road for all your upcoming adventures. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
