      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has had the critical 'big three' addressed: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced to prevent floor-pan fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, feeding power to a limited-slip differential. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral loads. Though it shows honest wear consistent with a driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust and the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. A visceral, analog machine for the technical purist.",
